description:
Modify src/engine/match/WeaponEngine.ts

Changes:
1. Update calculateDamage() to return explicit HitBreakdown[]
2. Support regen shield mechanics:
   - 100% absorption (vs 66% for light/heavy)
   - Track regen pool depletion
   - 3 second regen delay after depletion
3. Import from consolidated data files (weapons.ts, shields.ts)
4. Validate damage against weapon tables
5. Return remaining shield and HP after each hit

New signature:
calculateDamage(params: {
  weapon: WeaponProfile;
  distance: number;
  targetState: PlayerRoundState;
  shotCount: number;
  headshotProbability: number;
}): { hits: HitBreakdown[], targetStateAfter: PlayerRoundState }
